EnExplanation: A person who shows excessive compassion or mercy, often to the point of being overly lenient or indulgent.

Samples.EeSentence: Ülehalastaja on inimene, kes on alati valmis aitama teisi.
Samples.EnSentence: A benevolent person is someone who is always ready to help others.

Samples.EeSentence: Ülehalastaja aitab kõiki, kes vajavad abi.
Samples.EnSentence: The benefactor helps everyone in need.
